data.description: Welcome to 7211 Nichols Rd! This charming 3BD/3BA Basement Rancher w/finished basement rec room in the South Knox area is perfectly situated on a large lot of approximately .95 Acre. This home affords you total privacy behind not only with the .95 Acre Lot but also the tranquil in ground pool area that boasts a 16 X 32 In-Ground Pool & all privacy beyond that! When you arrive at this home the first thing you will notice is that you have plenty of extra room for parking on the upper & lower driveways. As you enter the home you will notice the durable Hardwood flooring in the main areas, which is perfect for high traffic or pets, the open family room with plenty of natural light, & the side deck/porch where you can enjoy a peaceful morning or relaxing in the afternoon/evenings. This functional floor plan boasts 3 Bedrooms, 3 Full Baths, a partially finished basement with large rec room & full bath, a 16 X 32 In-Ground Pool behind, a spacious Kitchen with ample Cabinet & Countertop Space, 3 BR's on the main level, & a spacious Family Room! This home also features a single car basement garage with a large laundry area & extra room for storage. Homes that offer this much do not come available often. It truly is a must see.
